These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-1::.
House: victorian, ranch-style, modern
3 different games are played: whist, backgammon, bridge
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: scientific, animation, crime
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: zinnia, azalea, begonia
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, tiparillo, swisher
There are 3 different nationalities: colombian, german, italian
City: edinburgh, colone, boston
 1. the person traveling to edinburgh is the german##1
 2. the person traveling to boston is the person who growsbegonia##1
 3. the modern house is between the italian and the ranch-style house##2
 4. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the colombian##1
 5. the person who growsazalea is the person playing bridge##1
 6. the person watching crime movies is the colombian##1
 7. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person playing whist##1
 8. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the game-smoker##1
 9. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
10. the person watching animation movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |
| House      | ranch-style    | modern   | victorian           |
| Game          | backgammon       | bridge    | whist         |
| Movie-Genre         | animation    | crime  | scientific        |
| Flower           | zinnia | azalea   | begonia      |
| Cigar   | tiparillo        | swisher    | game       |
| Nationality   | german     | colombian  | italian       |
| City         | edinburgh     | colone | boston |

