The people use 3 different means of transport: jet-ski, van, snowmobile
The people have 3 different jobs:  security-guard, pilot, fisherman
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, january, september
The people have 3 different hobbies: reading, filmmaking, traveling
3 different pets are kept: dog, horse, pony
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, zinnia, rose
 1. the owner of the pony is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 2. the owner of the pony is the fisherman##1
 3. the fisherman is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 4. the person who growslily is between the person playing canasta and the person playing domino##2
 5. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far left##1
 6. the person playing canasta is the person who's birthday is in april##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
 8. the person driving the jet-ski is the security-guard##1
 9. the fisherman is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
10. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| Game      | domino   | go    | canasta         |
| Transport          | jet-ski    | van | snowmobile          |
| Job   | security-guard  | fisherman  | pilot     |
| Birthday   | september       | january      | april         |
| Hobby   | traveling      | filmmaking   | reading    |
| Pet           | dog        | pony      | horse         |
| Flower         | zinnia | lily  | rose |

