There are 3 different favourite colors: yellow, aquamarine, fuchsia
3 different pets are kept: bird, fish, guinea-pig
The people have 3 different jobs:  social-worker, nurse, chef
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, january, may
 1. the chef is in the middle##1
 2. the fan of jazz is in the middle##1
 3. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 4. the person traveling to colone is the person who growsbegonia##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1
 6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in may is between the fan of metal and the person who likes yellow##2
 8. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the social-worker##1
 9. the person who growsbegonia is the person who's birthday is in february##1
10. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
11. the person who's birthday is in february is the person who likes yellow##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Music-Genre      | metal | jazz      | salsa      |
| City         | liverpool     | hamburg     | colone  |
| Flower   | poppy | aconite  | begonia |
| Color   | aquamarine  | fuchsia     | yellow |
| Pet           | bird        | guinea-pig | fish     |
| Job         | social-worker    | chef | nurse   |
| Birthday     | january        | may        | february   |

