.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-20::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, indie, funk
The people have 3 different hobbies: reading, collecting, woodworking
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: zinnia, balloon-flower, rose
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, ritmeester, pall-mall
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: drama, musical, zombie
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, november, march
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, jet-ski, roller
1. the fan of d&b is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the person driving the roller is the person who's birthday is in september##1
3. the person who growszinnia is between the fan of funk and the person watching zombie movies##2
4. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
5. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
6. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
7. the person who growsballoon-flower is the person who's hobby is reading##1
8. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
9. the ritmeester-smoker is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person driving the car##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Music-Genre      | indie    | d&b       | funk      |
| Hobby          | reading   | woodworking   | collecting  |
| Flower           | balloon-flower  | zinnia | rose    |
| Cigar   | old-henry   | ritmeester     | pall-mall  |
| Movie-Genre           | zombie     | drama        | musical |
| Birthday         | november | september   | march  |
| Transport     | jet-ski    | roller     | car      |

 